    33          Create(context.Context, *v1alpha1.StorageVersion, metav1.CreateOptions) (*v1alpha1.StorageVersion, error)
    34          UpdateStatus(context.Context, *v1alpha1.StorageVersion, metav1.UpdateOptions) (*v1alpha1.StorageVersion, error)
